# Cloudflare Pages routing.
#
# 1. Proxy /api/* to the FastAPI backend on Render. Without this rule,
#    /api/* falls through to the SPA's index.html and the frontend
#    can't reach the backend at all (push subscribe / chat / matches /
#    discover / pulse all silently fail).
# 2. SPA catch-all so React Router handles client-side routes.

/api/*   https://sonder-16mj.onrender.com/api/:splat   200

/*       /index.html                                    200
